Class Food

  • java.lang.Object
    • reading.kartik.ArtificialSimulator.AnEntity
      • reading.kartik.ArtificialSimulator.Food

  • public class Food
extends AnEntity
    This class extends AnEntity, and is used to create and store food objects in the world. Aside from its super parameters, it also has a tag variable, which stores whether the food is vegetarian or not.
